   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Germanos, quintanensis, to Lucius Dionysios, greetings.  I have the quintana of Pauni and Epeiph, total (dr.) 32.  Year 12 of Nero the lord, Epeiph 18.</ab>
